admesh
------------------------------------------
ADMesh is a program for processing triangulated solid meshes. Currently, ADMesh
only reads the STL file format that is used for rapid prototyping applications,
although it can write STL, VRML, OFF, and DXF files.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libadmesh-devel-0.98.4-1bl1
  libadmesh1-0.98.4-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/admesh/admesh

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/admesh/admesh/archive/v0.98.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack admesh-0.98.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./admesh-0.98.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/admesh-0.98.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/admesh-0.98.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libadmesh1-0.98.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libadmesh-devel-0.98.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(admesh)
  /usr/bin/admesh.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/admesh.README
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/ChangeLog.old
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/admesh/admesh-doc.txt
  /usr/share/man/man1/admesh.1.gz

(libadmesh1)
  /usr/bin/cygadmesh-1.dll

(libadmesh-devel)
  /usr/include/admesh/stl.h
  /usr/lib/libadmesh.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libadmesh.pc

